ty]]\n===Caucus memberships===\n* [[Climate Solutions Caucus]]<ref>{{cite web|title=90 Current Climate Solutions Caucus Members|author=|url=https://citizensclimatelobby.org/climate-solutions-caucus/|format=| publisher=Citizen\u00b4s Climate Lobby |date=|accessdate=18 October 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nRyan Costello lives along with his wife and two children in [[West Chester, Pennsylvania]].<ref name=th/> He is a [[Presbyterian Church (U.S.A.)|Presbyterian]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nationaljournal.com/almanac/2014-new-members/pennsylvania-6-ryan-costello-r-20141104 |title=Pennsylvania-6: Ryan Costello (R)|work=www.nationaljournal.com |accessdate=January 18, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Engagements: Thomas \u2013 Costello |url=http://www.dailylocal.com/article/DL/20110306/LIFE01/303069982 |publisher=Daily Local News |accessdate=January 5, 2015}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Portal|Biography|Pennsylvania}}\n* [http://costello.house.gov/ Congressman Ryan Costello] official U.S. House site\n* [https://www.ryancostelloforcongress.com/ Ryan Costello for Congress]\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Pennsylvania/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Ryan_Costello_%5BR-6%5D}}\n* {{C-SPAN|ryancostello}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio=C001106 | votesmart=133557 | fec=H0PA06076 | congress=ryan-costello/2266 }}<!--\nLinks formerly displayed via the CongLinks template:\n* [http://ballotpedia.org/Ryan Costello Biography] at [[Ballotpedia]]\n* [http://www.govtrack.us/congress/members/412651 Congressional profile] at [[GovTrack]]\n* [http://www.opencongress.org/people/show/412651 Congressional profile] at [[Participatory Politics Foundation|OpenCongress]]\n* [http://www.rollcall.com/members/53275.html Congressional profile] at ''[[Roll Call]]''\n* [http://www.ontheissues.org/MA/Ryan_Costello.htm Issue positions and quotes] at [[On the Issues]]\n* [http://www.c-spanvideo.org/ryancostello Appearances] on [[C-SPAN]] 